## PR Title Format:
**Use imperative style (NOT conventional commit format):**

PR titles should read like changelog entries for release notes.

### Format:
```
<imperative verb> <description> [optional scope or reference]
```

### Examples:
- ‚úÖ `Add user profile editing flow`
- ‚úÖ `Fix crash when user logs out`
- ‚úÖ `Implement authentication and user profiles (Epic 2.1)`
- ‚úÖ `Chat: Add message retry on network failure`
- ‚úÖ `[PROJ-421] Add offline message sync`
- ‚ùå `feat: add user authentication` (NO conventional commit prefix)
- ‚ùå `Added user authentication` (wrong tense - use imperative)
